                "title" => "RSUD CIMACAN IMPLEMENTASIKAN ELECTRONIC MEDICAL RECORD",
                "sub_desc" => "Electronic Medical Record (EMR) sudah diimplementasikan di Rumah Sakit Umum Daerah Cimacan pada hari Senin, 18 Juli 2022. ",
